<view class="page">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="eyebrow">traditional astrology lab</view>
    <view class="title">命理排盘工作台</view>
    <view class="summary">紫微斗数、四柱八字与 LLM 解读的移动入口。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="actions">
    <button class="primary" bindtap="openNativeApp">打开原生排盘</button>
    <view class="secondary-actions">
      <button class="secondary" bindtap="openWebApp">网页版完整盘</button>
      <button class="secondary" open-type="share">分享给朋友</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel">
    <view class="row" bindtap="openSettings">
      <view>
        <view class="row-title">设置与上线检查</view>
        <view class="row-text">保存后端访问密钥、复制微信平台域名</view>
      </view>
      <view class="chevron">›</view>
    </view>
    <view class="row" bindtap="openCompliance">
      <view>
        <view class="row-title">合规说明与使用边界</view>
        <view class="row-text">传统文化参考、隐私与模型解读说明</view>
      </view>
      <view class="chevron">›</view>
    </view>
    <view class="row" bindtap="copyUrl">
      <view>
        <view class="row-title">复制网页版地址</view>
        <view class="row-text">{{siteUrl}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="chevron">›</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="notice">
    原生版已接入 iztro 命盘摘要和 LLM 解读闭环；网页版完整盘继续保留，用于查看更完整盘面和备案路线。
  </view>
</view>
